      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be letting this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and treated like a member of the family. She\u2019s in truly stunning, showroom-quality shape. You might find a tiny, microscopic stone chip if you really go looking for one, but otherwise, she looks and drives like she just left the dealership. It\u2019s rare to find one kept this clean, and I\u2019d love for a fellow enthusiast to come by, grab a coffee, and see just how special she is!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
