    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a sanctuary of automotive excellence that feels less like a used vehicle and more like a preserved moment in time. The bodywork wears a luster so deep it mirrors the sky, while the interior carries that unmistakable, intoxicating scent of premium craftsmanship. Driving this isn't just about travel; it's about the way the world slows down as you glide through the gears, the engine singing a soulful melody that modern cars have long since forgotten. This is a rare opportunity to capture a masterpiece of design and engineering, a pristine companion ready to turn every mundane errand into a cinematic journey.",
      "price": 44800.0,
